Mutt/Addressbook version 0.03
=============================

This is going to be a nice and handy addressbook for Mutt and other console
based MUA's. It's designed to run smoothly together with procmail.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  XML::Simple
  Class::MethodMaker

